title: Grateful Dead Live at Compton Terrace Amphitheatre on 1987-08-18
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Walkin' Blues, Ramble On Rose, My Brother Esau, Peggy-O, Greatest Story Ever Told, Bertha

Set 2

Crazy Fingers-> Playing In the Band -> Terrapin Station -> Drums -> Space -> Dear Mr. Fantasy -> Wharf Rat -> Throwing Stones -> Turn On Your Lovelight, E: Black Muddy River

reviews.review_text:
Great Recording & Show As always the Oade Brothers come through with an incredible AUD recording. Reminds me more of a Matrix than straight AUD because of the beautiful clarity. I would recommend this recording as "the" source. Very well rounded.

On top of that, the Dead put on an awesome show. The second set is the perfect example of what Summer '87 was all about.
